headline.main: RUSSIA 'ANNEXED,' FUNK TELLS NAZIS; Reich Minister Sees Economic Gain for 'New Europe' in Vast Russian Lands

lead_paragraph: KOENIGSBERG, Germany, Oct. 12 -- By their victorious progress In Russia, Reichsfuehrer Hitler's armies are opening up new valuable markets for German industries after the war, according to an address delivered here today by Dr. Walther Funk, Reich Minister of Economics and President of the Reichsbank.
abstract: Min Funk on gains from USSR conquests
